summary: 6 new world spaces, 40 new npcs, new camps, dwellings, and cities....This is Farreach
descriptionHtml:
Some Storm cloak soldiers left Skyrim before the war was over and were seen heading north to find new lands. Whether they found it or not no one has ever known...Until now board the ship at dawnstar and head north into the lands and islands of Farreach.

This is a new land for you to explore. There are no quests at this point. But I will add player homes to 4 of the 6 world spaces soon. 

Make your way through marshes, deadly highlands, and mountain passes

:

6 new world spaces, 40 new npcs, new camps, dwellings, and cities....This is Farreach 

This mod is pretty heavy and might clash with any new land, or new place mods you might have installed.

I recommend using:
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=17426 - AI Archery Range Increase

http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=9063 - Killmove plus

Bring a bow to Farreach :) or you will not survive!]

Let me know if it works for you!

Also please upload any pics u take!


install by dropping it in to Computer/local c disk/programs files x86/ steam/ steam apps/ common/ skyrim/ data

Known gliches: There might be some landscaping issues within the marshes, nothing to big
